@startuml
title 荧光伪彩与通道融合 - 时序图

actor "操作者" as User
participant "ChannelPanel" as Panel
participant "DyeLibraryService" as DyeService
participant "ChannelFusionService" as FusionService
participant "ChannelFusionEngine" as Engine
participant "ObservationSession" as Session
participant "ImageViewport" as View
participant "ProjectDocument" as Project

User -> Panel: 选择单通道图像
Panel -> DyeService: listDyes()
DyeService --> Panel: DyeProfile 列表
User -> Panel: 选择染料/颜色并调节强度范围
Panel -> FusionService: setChannel(channel)
FusionService -> FusionService: build ChannelFusionRecipe
User -> Panel: 应用融合
Panel -> FusionService: applyRecipe(recipe)
FusionService -> Engine: fuse(recipe)
Engine --> FusionService: RGB display frame
FusionService --> Panel: fused ImageFrame
Panel -> Session: setDisplayFrame(frame)
Session -> View: setDisplayImage(frame)
Session -> Project: save recipe and channel metadata
View -> View: repaint without changing raw source frames

@enduml
